definitions.definition: A variety of Spanish small savoury food items or snacks such as croquettes , cured meat , potato salad , and seafood , originally served with sherry and now often with other alcoholic beverages as well.

main_definition: A variety of Spanish small savoury food items or snacks such as croquettes , cured meat , potato salad , and seafood , originally served with sherry and now often with other alcoholic beverages as well.
